These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: card-games, collecting
Movie-Genre: scientific, adventure
1. Movie-Genre:scientific is in an even position##4
2. Movie-Genre:adventure == Hobby:collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games |
| Movie-Genre     | adventure    | scientific   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Transport: roller, scooter
Sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. Sport:sailing is in an odd position##4
2. Transport:scooter is on the left of Transport:roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Transport   | scooter | roller        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Food: carrot, cherry
Nationality: canadian, turkish
1. Nationality:canadian is in an odd position##4
2. Food:cherry is on the left of Food:carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Food   | cherry    | carrot |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish |

